description: Demolition of existing commercial buildings and erection of 5 x 2/3/4 storey buildings and two linked buildings comprising 15 x 1 bed, 30 x 2 bed and 9 x 3 bed apartments and 9 x 3 bed, 5 x 4 bed and 1 x 5 bed houses with associated parking and amenity space. Provision of new access road and improvements to Weir Road, formation of footpath link alongside River Cray with associated landscaping.
